               <h1>Request for Change Program</h1>  
            <hr>

               <div class="content">
               <div itemprop="articleBody"><table> <tbody> <tr> <td><strong>Change Program Process for Incoming Freshmen</strong></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p><em>Guidelines for Change Course/Program Request</em><em><br> <br> The following rules are implemented in processing the approval of request for change course/program.<br> </em><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong><br></strong>1.&nbsp;<em>Returnee-Shiftee and upperclassmen are not allowed in this procedure. Kindly ask your respective college or&nbsp;</em><em>department for the&nbsp;upperclassmen&nbsp;shiftee enrollment process. This portal should be accessed only by qualified incoming freshmen that are still in the admissions phase.</em></p><p>2<em>.&nbsp;</em><em>A student is allowed to file request for change course/program only “once”.</em></p><p>3.<em>&nbsp;</em>Engineering<em> (except IE), </em>Nursing<em>, </em>Accountancy<em>, </em>AB/BS Psychology<em> and </em>Education<em> programs will not consider&nbsp;</em><em>applicants who are requesting for change of course/program from any of those under “waived” entrance examination if they have not taken the entrance exam and meet the cutoff score for the course/program&nbsp;</em><em>they are requesting to change to.&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p> <em> <br> </em></td> </tr> </tbody> </table><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step1</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></strong>Access this link <a href="https://forms.gle/KGxyM4zXE1LwDA9w6">https://forms.gle/KGxyM4zXE1LwDA9w6</a> to register request for Change Program.</p><p>Upload clear scanned copy or photo of the following:</p><ol> <li><strong>Admissions Clearance</strong> or <strong>For Consideration Letter</strong> (for <strong>CONDITIONAL</strong> applicant)</li> </ol><ol start="2"> <li>Grade 12 Report Card</li> </ol><p><strong>Step2&nbsp; <br></strong>Once changing of course/program is approved, the <strong>New Admissions Clearance</strong> will be sent to you via email. Please check both your INBOX and SPAM folders.</p><p><strong>Step3 &nbsp; <br></strong>Pay the required down payment of Php3,000.00</p><p>Go to this link <a href="/payment-centers-finance"><strong>https://www.xu.edu.ph/payment-centers-finance</strong></a> to view the list of accredited&nbsp;XU payment centers.</p><ul> <li><strong>IMPORTANT: </strong>Secure ADMISSIONS CLEARANCE prior to making a down payment. Carefully follow the instructions in filling out the bank forms as indicated on the Admissions Clearance.</li> </ul><p><strong>Step4 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br></strong>Process <strong>Online Enrolment Registration</strong> of your school/college by accessing this link <strong>https://www.xu.edu.ph/admissions-enrollment</strong></p><ul> <li>After completing the online registration, a notification will be sent to you&nbsp;via email regarding the status of your application for enrollment in XU.&nbsp;If successful, you will be given your Login credentials to access the Student&nbsp;Lifecycle Management and Information System (SLMIS) to check your class&nbsp;schedule and other related information.</li> </ul><div class="bt-social-share bt-social-share-below"><div class="bt-social-share-button bt-facebook-share-button"><fb:share-button href="https://www.xu.edu.ph/admission-changeprogram" type="button_count" class=" fb_iframe_widget" fb-xfbml-state="rendered" fb-iframe-plugin-query="app_id=&amp;container_width=0&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xu.edu.ph%2Fadmission-changeprogram&amp;locale=en_GB&amp;sdk=joey&amp;type=button_count"><span style="vertical-align: bottom; width: 77px; height: 20px;"><iframe name="f2b4a9dc86131bc" width="1000px" height="1000px" data-testid="fb:share_button Facebook Social Plugin" title="fb:share_button Facebook Social Plugin" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allowfullscreen="true" scrolling="no" allow="encrypted-media" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/share_button.php?app_id=&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fx%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter%2F%3Fversion%3D46%23cb%3Df16076f586a381%26domain%3Dwww.xu.edu.ph%2